## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and does not include the most recent developments or studies published after this date. Additionally, while the sources used are reputable, the complexity of climate change means that its impacts can vary significantly by region and demographic, which may not be fully captured in this report. Further research is recommended to explore localized effects and mitigation strategies.